### LXVIII. HOW SUNRISE.

<span id="img_08501"></span> ![](img/08501.jpg)

To express *sunrise* they depict the TWO EYES OF A CROCODILE,

<span id="page_86">p. 86</span>

because of the whole body of the animal its eyes glare conspicuously
from the deep.

